com.samsung.android.sdk.visualview

Class SV

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.sdk.visualview.SV
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SsdkInterface

    public class SV
extends Object
implements SsdkInterface
    This class provides access to the Visual View Package.

    The Class Provides the Version Code, the Version name and the initialization methods for the Visual View package. It also provides different interpolator types.

    You can use the interpolators to control the animation speed and acceleration
